Function Reference/ cleanup header comment Â« WordPress Codex
-----------

**\_cleanup\_header\_comment** does strip close comment and close php
tags from file headers used by WP (See [Ticket
\#8497](http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/8497 "http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/8497"))

It is a [File Header](/File_Header "File Header") related function in
the global namespace within WordPress.

More in [WordPress \_cleanup\_header\_comment function
documentation](http://phpdoc.wordpress.org/trunk/WordPress/_wp-includes---functions.php.html#function_cleanup_header_comment "http://phpdoc.wordpress.org/trunk/WordPress/_wp-includes---functions.php.html#function_cleanup_header_comment")

